Bundled simpleperf Gecko conversion runtime
===========================================

This directory vendors selected files from Android NDK simpleperf
version 29.0.13113456 to convert `perf.data` into Gecko profile JSON.

Source:
- Android Open Source Project / Android NDK simpleperf

Included components:
- `gecko_profile_generator.py`
- `simpleperf_report_lib.py`
- `simpleperf_utils.py`
- `report_sample_pb2.py`
- `profile_pb2.py`
- `bin/darwin/x86_64/libsimpleperf_report.dylib`

